{
  "texts": [
    "In both POSG-Comm and Dec-POMDP-Comm, action policies take into account both environmental observations and inter-agent messages.",
    "Research works in Comm-MADRL that expand upon a POSG or a Dec-POMDP can be seen in references such as [60,62,[64][65][66].",
    "Communication in recent surveysCommunication has attracted much attention in the field of multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL).",
    "Previous surveys mentioning communication in MARL primarily focus on providing an overview of MARL's development.",
    "These surveys view communication as a subfield in MARL, and no extensive and substantial progress is reported."
  ]
}